The block is taken to start at the first letter of the begin keyword and
to end after the end keyword."
  (let ((pos (point)))
    (save-excursion
      (condition-case nil
	  (progn
	    (skip-syntax-forward "w")
	    (octave-up-block -1)
	    (octave-forward-block)
	    t)
	(error nil))
      (< pos (point)))))

